orted%20%26quot%3Bbad%20trips%26quot%3B%20on%20both%20LSD%20and%20ecstasy.%20There%20could%20be%20risks%20involved%20with%20using%20psychedelics%2C%20and%20research%20is%20still%20being%20done%20to%20evaluate%20therapeutic%20uses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBarry%2C%20now%20my%20husband%2C%20was%20the%20person%20who%20introduced%20me%20to%20LSD%20almost%2050%20years%20ago%20when%20I%20was%2023.%20We%20were%20camping%20one%20summer%20at%20Manning%20Park%2C%20one%20of%20British%20Columbia's%20provincial%20parks%2C%20and%20we%20each%20took%20acid%20as%20we%20strolled%20along%20a%20gently%20winding%20trail%20called%20Lightning%20Lakes.%20I%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhow-to-smoke-weed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esmoked%20grass%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20before%2C%20but%20nothing%20psychedelic%20%E2%80%94%20in%20fact%2C%20I%20had%20been%20afraid%20of%20it%20until%20Barry%20told%20me%20how%20transformational%20his%20first%20trip%20had%20been.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%20that%20day%2C%20while%20we%20ate%20apple%20pie%20at%20the%20park%20restaurant%2C%20Barry%20scribbled%20on%20a%20napkin%2C%20%26quot%3BLouisa%20is%20treating%20herself%20very%20delicately%2C%20like%20porcelain%20china.%26quot%3B%20Later%20still%2C%20we%20went%20up%20to%20a%20lookout.%20As%20we%20sat%20watching%20the%20fading%20light%2C%20he%20turned%20to%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20Sarah%20Louisa.%26quot%3B%20Hearing%20him%20address%20me%20using%20my%20first%20name%20brought%20tears%20to%20my%20eyes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEver%20since%2C%20psychedelics%20have%20been%20an%20essential%20companion%20in%20our%20relationship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20rarely%20outed%20myself%20as%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-cluster-headaches-taking-lsd-improved-pain-netflix-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Euser%20of%20psychedelics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20until%20Michael%20Pollan%20popularized%20it%20in%20his%20best-selling%20book%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20Change%20Your%20Mind%3A%20What%20the%20New%20Science%20of%20Psychedelics%20Teaches%20Us%20About%20Consciousness%2C%20Dying%2C%20Addiction%2C%20Depression%2C%20and%20Transcendence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20I've%20become%20increasingly%20open%20about%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBarry%20and%20I%20use%20psychedelics%20on%20average%20two%20or%20three%20times%20a%20year.%20Our%20experience%20ranges%20wildly%2C%20from%20silliness%20and%20laughter%20%E2%80%94%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20laughed%20more%20in%20one%20day%20than%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20in%2010%20years%20%E2%80%94%20to%20tearful%2C%20poignant%2C%20and%20serious%2C%20sometimes%20all%20of%20that%20in%20one%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6656ecd-f198-4a58-82d0-58623382bf20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20helps%20us%20have%20difficult%20conversations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThrough%20much%20practice%20and%20commitment%2C%20we%20have%20developed%20an%20open%2C%20honest%20communication%20style%2C%20and%20we%20can%20have%20hard%20conversations%20without%20being%20high.%20But%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychedelics-work-microdosing-lsd-psilocybin-ketamine-retreats-elon-musk-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eadvantage%20of%20psychedelics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20in%20the%20form%20of%20acid%20or%20ecstasy%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20they%20help%20us%20to%20be%20vulnerable%20by%20quickly%20dropping%20our%20defenses%2C%20listening%20to%20each%20other%20more%20easily%2C%20and%20hearing%20the%20unpleasant%20truths%20that%20the%20other%20might%20offer.%20Without%20psychedelics%2C%20the%20conversa