A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-assembly-passes-anti-paper-leak-bill-rs-10-lakh-fine-prison-term-6177535%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-assembly-passes-anti-paper-leak-bill-rs-10-lakh-fine-prison-term-6177535%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shambhu%20Blockade%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Flags%20Farmers-Government%20'Trust%20Deficit'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20trust%20deficit%20between%20farmers%20protesting%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border%20and%20the%20government%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20must%20take%20steps%20to%20reach%20out%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today.%20The%20court%20was%20hearing%20matters%20related%20to%20the%20farmers'%20protest%20and%20the%20blockade%20at%20Shambhu%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20take%20some%20steps%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20farmers.%20Why%20would%20they%20otherwise%20want%20to%20come%20to%20Delhi%3F%20You%20are%20sending%20ministers%20from%20here%20and%20despite%20their%20best%20intentions%2C%20there%20is%20a%20trust%20deficit.%20They%20will%20think%20you%20are%20only%20talking%20about%20self-interest%20and%20ignoring%20local%20issues.%20Why%20don't%20you%20send%20a%20neutral%20umpire%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant%20and%20Justice%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Haryana%20government%2C%20said%20the%20state%20has%20no%20problem%20with%20the%20farmers'%20march%20to%20Delhi.%20%26quot%3BBut%20coming%20with%20tanks%2C%20JCBs%20(excavators)%20causes%20friction.%20Earlier%2C%20it%20was%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20farm%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20farmers'%20protest%20in%202020-21%20that%20forced%20the%20Centre%20to%20roll%20back%20three%20farm%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20has%20challenged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20a%20high%20court%20order%20to%20remove%20barricades%20at%20Shambhu%20border%20within%20a%20week.%20The%20barricades%20were%20put%20in%20place%20this%20February%20after%20several%20farmers'%20outfits%20announced%20a%20march%20to%20Delhi%20to%20press%20for%20several%20demands%2C%20including%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20for%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20for%20crops.%20The%20border%20crossing%20also%20saw%20clashes%20between%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20and%20security%20personnel%20blocking%20their%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20the%20highway%20cannot%20remain%20blocked%20for%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%20said%20he%20is%20only%20seeking%20a%20pause%20on%20the%20high%20court%20direction%20to%20Haryana.%20%26quot%3BEven%20as%20a%20welfare%20state%2C%20we%20cannot%20afford%20untoward%20things%20when%20dealing%20with%20sensitive%20matters.%20These%20are%20prohibited%20only%20on%20national%20highway.%20No%20Act%20permits.%20MV%20(Motor%20Vehicles)%20Act%20prohibits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20asked%20if%20there%20is%20a%20prohibition%20on%20excavators%20and%20tractors%20crossing%20the%20border%2C%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BJCBs%20are%20converted%20into%20virtual%20war%20tanks.%20I%20am%20saying%20this%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20responsibility.%20Armoured%20vehicles%2C%20we%20have%20photographs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab's%20Attorney%20General%20Gurminder%20Singh%20said%20the%20highway%20blockade%20has%20huge%20ramifications%20for%20the%20state's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20then%20proposed%20a%20committee%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20farmers%20and%20build%20consensus%20between%20them%2C%20Haryana%20government%20and%20the%20Centre.%20The%20committee%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20their%20viewpoints%2C%20know%20and%20tell%20them%20where%20they%20are%20right%20and%20wrong%26