20for%20JD%20Vance%20to%20become%20vice-president%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBowing%20before%20a%20silver%20cloth-wrapped%20idol%20of%20Sai%20Baba%2C%20the%20priest%20seeks%20blessings%20for%20the%20Republican%20politician%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Usha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVadluru%2C%20a%20quiet%20village%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20a%20canal%20deep%20in%20the%20verdant%20countryside%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20is%20the%20ancestral%20home%20of%20Vance's%20wife%2C%20who%20will%20become%20the%20US%20Second%20Lady%20--%20and%20the%20first%20who%20is%20not%20white%20--%20if%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20elected%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20bless%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20priest%2C%20whose%20temple%20is%20in%20a%20building%20once%20owned%20by%20Usha's%20family%2C%20the%20Chilukuris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20should%20get%20higher%20positions%20in%20her%20life.%20We%20priests%20offer%20special%20prayers%20for%20Usha%20and%20her%20husband.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha's%20great-grandfather%20moved%20out%20of%20Vadluru%2C%20but%20her%20ancestors%20are%20respected%20in%20the%20village%20as%20academic%20highflyers%20and%20well-versed%20in%20Hindu%20scriptures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%20Chilukuri%20Radhakrishnan%20--%20a%20PhD%20holder%20--%20was%20brought%20up%20in%20Chennai%20and%20went%20on%20to%20study%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20He%20returned%20to%20India%20before%20the%20couple%20moved%20back%20across%20the%20Pacific%2C%20and%20Usha%20was%20brought%20up%20in%20suburban%20San%20Diego.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20met%20Vance%20at%20Yale%20Law%20School%20and%20the%20couple%20married%20in%202014.%20They%20have%20three%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHillbilly%20Elegy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%20Vance%20has%20never%20visited%20the%20village%2C%20but%20the%20priest%20said%20her%20father%20last%20came%20around%20three%20years%20ago%20and%20checked%20on%20temple's%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELittle%20is%20kno