%20to%20the%20village%20temple's%20upkeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20600%20kilometres%20away%20from%20Vadluru%2C%20Usha's%20great-grandaunt%20Chilukuri%20Santhamma%20sat%20hunched%20over%20a%20pile%20of%20papers%20as%20she%20called%20on%20her%20relative%20to%20urge%20others%20not%20to%20follow%20in%20her%20family's%20footsteps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20of%20the%20family%20academics%2C%20at%2096%20she%20is%20hailed%20in%20local%20media%20as%20the%20country's%20oldest%20active%20professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20related%20to%20Usha%20through%20her%20husband%2C%20an%20academic%20himself%20who%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%20should%20use%20her%20position%20and%20legal%20knowledge%20to%20stop%20the%20%26quot%3Bdrain%26quot%3B%20of%20Indians%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Santhamma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can%20go%20for%20education%2C%20they%20can%20go%20for%20training%2C%20all%20this%20they%20can%20do%20but%20there%20is%20a%20limitation.%20They%20have%20to%20stay%20there%20for%20known%20time%20and%20come%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20believes%20Usha%20has%20a%20tough%20life%2C%20despite%20being%20married%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20person%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20become%20the%20wife%20of%20a%20great%20person%20is%20the%20fortune%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20but%20has%20%26quot%3Btaken%20politics%20as%20her%20subject%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20a%20very%20tough%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721813520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F6e2p4ghg_usha-vance-andhra_625x300_24_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F