.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0held%20once%20every%20five%20years%20%E2%80%94%20was%20closely%20watched%20because%20the%20world's%20second-largest%20economy%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20claw%20itself%20out%20of%20an%20epic%20property%20crisis%20post-pandemic%2C%20and%20its%20once-mighty%20consumers%20are%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-luxury-retail-sales-slowdown-brands-fashion-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20splashing%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20much%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20called%20the%20Third%20Plenum%2C%20Beijing%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.cn%2Fpolitics%2F20240721%2Fcec09ea2bde840dfb99331c48ab5523a%2Fc.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elengthy%20document%3C%2Fa%3E%20spanning%2022%2C000%20Chinese%20characters.%20Economists%20and%20analysts%20have%20tried%20to%20read%20between%20the%20lines%20%E2%80%94%20with%20much%20difficulty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20you%20attribute%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20significance%20to%20Beijing's%20'Five-Sphere%20Integrated%20Plan'%20or%20the%20'Four-Pronged%20Comprehensive%20Strategy%2C'%20the%20plenum's%20communique%20was%20long%20on%20slogans%20and%20short%20on%20substance%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Lubin%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20fellow%20of%20global%20economy%20and%20finance%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chathamhouse.org%2F2024%2F07%2Fchinas-third-plenum-watch-what-they-do-not-what-they-say%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatham%20House%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20London-based%20think%20tank%2C%20wrote%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20it's%20what%20he%20calls%20a%20problem%20of%20%26quot%3Bthey%20just%20don't%20say%20very%20much%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff62c6a4-99ba-4301-b703-a37fdf15184f%5C%22%3ESlogans%20over%20actions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20that%20unusual%20a%20situation%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Ffinance-and-economics%2F2024%2F01%2F11%2Fa-guide-to-the-chinese-communist-partys-economic-jargon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeijing%20loves%20slogans.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20slogans%20also%20do%20%26quot%3Bdo%20genuinely%20reflect%20deep%20thinking%20about%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20Lubin%20acknowledged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Beijing%20officials%20talk%20about%20'the%20new%20development%20philosophy'%2C%20'Chinese%20modernization'%2C%20'high%20quality%20development'%2C%20'new%20quality%20productive%20forces'%2C%20or%20a%20'high-standards%20socialist%20market%20economy'%2C%20these%20are%20references%20to%20real%20objectives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%2C%20Third%20Plenums%20also%20tend%20to%20focus%20on%20long-term%20economic%20policy%20and%20reforms%2C%20but%20the%20message%20of%20continuity%20this%20time%20isn't%20quite%20the%20jolt%20markets%20were%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20and%20investors%20were%20disappointed%20because%20there%20wasn't%20enough%20clarity%20or%20detail%20about%20what%20authorities%20are%20going%20to%20do%20to%20tackle%20the%20challenges%20facing%20China's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20fixates%20on%20what%20Beijing%20wants%20to%20happen%20without%20explaining%20how%20it%20will%20do%20it.%20The%20package%20is%20not%20coherent.%20It%20also%20doubles%20down%20on%20policies%20raising%20alarm%20bells%20globally%20about%20China's%20growth%20model%20and%20persistent%20macroeconomic%20imbalances%2C%26quot%3B%20Rhodium%20Group%20analysts%20Daniel%20Rosen%20and%20Logan%20Wright%20wrote%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csis.org%2Fblogs%2Fthird-plenum-hot-takes-skepticism-and-concern%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECenter%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20engineer%20a%20painful%20economic%20transition%20from%20one%20reliant%20on%20real%20estate%20and%20lower-end%20manufacturing%20to%20the%20hot%20new%20sectors%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-new-growth-areas-electric-vehicles-batteries-solar-property-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20vehicles%2C%20batteries%2C%20and%20solar%20cells.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2200c636bc-8aac-4f8c-b418-f0f65a05eae8%5C%22%3EThird%20Plenum%20did%20not%20address%20consumption%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-second-quarter-gdp-growth-weak-demand-consumption-exports-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomy%20grew%204.7%25%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20year%20ago.%20Exports%20were%20a%20bright%20spot%2C%20but%20consumption%20sentiment%20has%20been%20extremely%20poor%2C%20with%20people%20preferring%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-household-deposits-savings-luxury-consumer-demand-slowdown-economy-outlook-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20spend%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20boost%20economic%20growth%20by%20driving%20domestic%20consumption%20through%20subsidies%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinadaily.com.cn%2Fa%2F202406%2F03%2FWS665d241fa31082fc043ca884.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etrade-in%20deals%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20for%20property%20purchases.%20However%2C%20success%20has%20been%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeasures%20to%20boost%20domestic%20demand%20and%20consumption%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20missing%20part%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Third%20Plenum%2C%20Yue%20Su%2C%20the%20principal%20China%20economist%20at%20the%20Economist%20Intelligence%20Unit%2C%20said%20in%20a%20webinar%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20stimulus%20to%20boost%20household%20sector%20confidence%2C%20we%20observe%20a%20really%20bumpy%20recovery%20trend%20in%20consumption%20and%20retail%20sales.%20We%20continue%20to%20expect%20this%20trend%20to%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatham%20House's%20Lubin%20attributes%20Beijing's%20reluctance%20to%20stimulate%20household%20spending%20to%20fears%20that%20public%20debt%20may%20get%20so%20big%20that%20it%20would%20threaten%20financial%20stability%20and%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20all%20this%20adds%20up%20to%20is%20an%20exceptionally%20defensive%20approach%20to%20managing%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20the%20best%20way%20to%20explain%20this%20is%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20geopolitical%20challenges%20that%20Beijing%20sees%20itself%20confronted%20by%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Chatham%20House's%20Lubin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-third-plenum-plan-details-lacking-why2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721813495000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a063342d66759f66fd9c49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-third-plenum-plan-details-lacking-why2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22David%20Lubin%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20fellow%20of%20global%20economy%20and%20finance%20at%20Chatham%20House%2C%20said%20the%20plenum%20was%20%26quot%3Blong%20on%20slogans%20and%20short%20on%20substance.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-third-plenum-plan-details-lacking-why2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Graphic%20footage%20shows%20US%20officers%20stood%20over%20body%20of%20Trump%20gunman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A172