ts%20conceals%20a%20parking%20garage%20in%20the%20middle.%20In%20growing%20cities%20across%20the%20US%2C%20doughnuts%20are%20everywhere.%20In%20Gannon's%20eyes%2C%20they're%20clumsy%20solutions%20to%20our%20housing%20woes%3A%20The%20imposing%20structures%20offer%20little%20outdoor%20space%20and%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20precious%20land.%20It's%20much%20harder%20to%20find%20smaller%20apartment%20or%20condo%20buildings%2C%20the%20kind%20that%20might%20fit%20snugly%20between%20a%20single-family%20home%20and%20a%20local%20restaurant.%20Cities%20are%20full%20of%20these%20little%20parcels%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finclusionary-zoning-failing-low-income-residents-affordable-housing-crisis-solution-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bmissing%20middle%26quot%3B%20housing%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20bigger%20than%20a%20single-family%20home%20but%20much%20smaller%20than%20the%20popular%20doughnut%20%E2%80%94%20just%20isn't%20getting%20built.%20This%20reality%20is%20especially%20frustrating%20for%20pro-development%20yes-in-my-backyard%20activists%20who%20have%20spent%20years%20rewriting%20laws%20in%20hopes%20of%20encouraging%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuburbs-millennials-walkable-towns-cities-housing-affordability-loneliness-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edenser%2C%20more-diverse%20housing%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20some%20baby%20carrots%20to%20go%20with%20all%20those%20doughnuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20quest%20to%20build%20more%20and%20bring%20down%20costs%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyimbys-winning-lower-house-prices-rents-build-more-homes-neighborhoods-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYIMBYs%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20identified%20one%20overlooked%20hang-up%3A%20stairs.%20Yes%2C%20the%20humble%20stairwell%20is%20an%20unlikely%20but%20powerful%20foe.%20More%20specifically%2C%20they're%20taking%20aim%20at%20a%20widespread%20rule%20that%20requires%20almost%20every%20new%20apartment%20building%20in%20the%20US%20to%20include%20at%20least%20two%20separate%20stairwells.%20This%20part%20of%20local%20codes%2C%20they%20say%2C%20is%20an%20outdated%20safety%20measure%20that%20really%20just%20makes%20apartment%20units%20smaller%2C%20more%20expensive%2C%20and%20darker%20(yes%2C%20darker).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20developers%20are%20forced%20to%20devote%20more%20square%20footage%20to%20stairs%2C%20that%20means%20less%20space%20for%20living%20rooms%20or%20bedrooms.%20Entire%20units%20might%20end%20up%20on%20the%20cutting-room%20floor.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20wasted%20square%20footage%20is%20enough%20to%20hamstring%20the%20builder's%20profit%20and%20sink%20a%20project.%20Instead%20of%20getting%20much-needed%20housing%2C%20we%20get%20none.%20Tweaking%20building%20codes%20wouldn't%20mean%20sacrificing%20safety%20in%20the%20name%20of%20efficiency.%20In%20a%20moderately%20sized%20apartment%20building%20of%20five%20or%20six%20stories%2C%20advocates%20argue%2C%20a%20single%20stairwell%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20latest%20fire-stopping%20materials%2C%20sprinkler%20systems%2C%20and%20limits%20on%20the%20number%20of%20units%2C%20is%20more%20than%20enough%20to%20ensure%20safety.%20In%20fact%2C%20moving%20to%20this%20type%20of%20layout%20would%20bring%20American%20apartments%20in%20line%20with%20European%20and%20Asian%20countries%20that%20have%20allowed%20this%20kind%20of%20development%20for%20decades.%20When%20Gannon%20learned%20of%20the%20single-stair%20movement%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20said%2C%20everything%20clicked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20my%20god%2C'%26quot%3B%20Gannon%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BA%20light%20went%20on%2C%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20this%20is%20why%20apartments%20in%20the%20States%20suck.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20a%20few%20US%20cities%2C%20most%20notably%20Seattle%20and%20New%20York%20City%2C%20allow%20single-stair%20buildings%20to%20stretch%20up%20to%20six%20stories%20%E2%80%94%20pretty%20much%20everywhere%20else%20in%20America%20caps%20it%20at%20three.%20But%20the%20single-stair%20movement%20is%20gathering%20steam%20in%20places%20like%20Austin%2C%20where%20the%20City%20Council%20recently%20directed%20city%20planners%20to%20look%20into%20updating%20the%20building%20code%2C%20as%20well%20as%20entire%20states%20like%20California%20and%20Minnesota.%20Embracing%20the%20single%20stair%20could%20enable%20apartment%20buildings%20to%20squeeze%20into%20vacant%20lots%20that%20might%20otherwise%20have%20turned%20into%20single-family%20houses%20or%20sat%20undeveloped.%20It%20would%20also%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20build%20larger%20units%20for%20families%2C%20who%20are%20mostly%20ignored%20in%20the%20apartment%20market.%20More%20apartments%20and%20condos%20would%20mean%20lower%20costs%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20goal%2C%20anyway.%20These%20are%20stairs%20we're%20talking%20about%2C%20not%20a%20silver%20bullet%20for%20the%20housing%20crisis.%20But%20this%20obscure%20part%20of%20the%20building%20code%20wields%20huge%20influence%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20how%20our%20buildings%20look%20and%20feel%20and%20whether%20they%20even%20get%20built.%20Every%20new%20apartment%20building%20needs%20stairs%2C%20sure.%20But%20maybe%20we%20could%20do%20with%20a%20lot%20fewer%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EStairs%20are%20a%20relatively%20new%20obsession%20in%20YIMBYland.%20For%20years%2C%20crusaders%20against%20the%20housing%20shortage%20focused%20on%20dismantling%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-zoning-map-home-prices-down-real-estate-new-houses-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunholy%20mess%20of%20local%20zoning%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-housing-prices-shortage-apartment-rent-zoning-policies-support-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprohibited%20anything%20but%20single-family%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20fought%20against%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouston-building-cheap-new-starter-homes-real-estate-construction-lots-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eminimum%20lot%20sizes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20encouraged%20sprawl%20rather%20than%20density.%20Pro-development%20advocates%20scored%20significant%20victories%20%E2%80%94%20several%20states%2C%20including%20Washington%20and%20Oregon%2C%20have%20basically%20gotten%20rid%20of%20single-family%20zoning%20altogether.%20While%20it's%20one%20thing%20to%20change%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%2C%20the%20thornier%20question%20was%20how%20to%20get%20developers%20to%20actually%20build%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20raise%20the%20floor-area%20ratios%2C%20raise%20the%20height%20limits%2C%20lot%20coverage%2C%20whatever%2C%26quot%3B%20Stephen%20Smith%2C%20a%20building-code%20researcher%20and%20single-stair%20advocate%20who%20founded%20the%20Center%20for%20Building%20in%20North%20America%2C%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BBut%20you're%20still%20not%20going%20to%20get%20that%2C%20like%2C%20beautiful%201970s%20Italian%20apartment%20that%20you%20stayed%20in%20an%20Airbnb%20once.%20Buildings%20are%20just%20not%20like%20that%20in%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20things%20like%20stairs%20come%20in.%20Say%20you're%20a%20developer%20with%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20land%20in%20a%20quaint%20neighborhood.%20It's%20already%20the%20stuff%20of%20YIMBY%20dreams%3A%20The%20streets%20are%20lined%20with%20a%20blend%20of%20single-family%20homes%20and%20low-slung%20apartment%20buildings.%20Walk%20down%20the%20block%2C%20and%20you'll%20find%20restaurants%20and%20a%20grocery%20store.%20It's%20a%2020-minute%20bike%20ride%20from%20downtown.%20The%20dream%20would%20be%20to%20take%20this%20land%20and%20build%20it%20up%2C%20turning%20the%20vacant%20parcel%20into%20a%20condo%20or%20apartment%20building%20where%20more%20people%20could%20enjoy%20this%20breezy%20lifestyle.%20But%20your%20lot%20is%20small%20%E2%80%94%20only%203%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20or%20about%20one-third%20of%20the%20typical%20lot%20size%20for%20a%20new%20single-family%20home.%20From%20a%20pure%20profit%20perspective%2C%20the%20project%20makes%20sense%20only%20if%20you%20can%20squeeze%20in%20enough%20units%20to%20get%20a%20good%20return%20on%20investment%2C%20which%20means%20building%20higher%20than%20three%20stories.%20According%20to%20the%20building%20code%2C%20however%2C%20you'd%20have%20to%20include%20two%20stairwells%20at%20opposite%20ends%20of%20the%20building%2C%20with%20a%20corridor%20running%20between%20them.%20This%20eats%20up%20so%20much%20square%20footage%20that%20the%20project%20goes%20poof%20%E2%80%94%20the%20areas%20of%20each%20floor%20simply%20can't%20accommodate%20the%20necessary%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Texas%20doughnut%20is%20a%20product%20of%20these%20limitations.%20Instead%20of%20building%20on%20small%20lots%2C%20developers%20are%20pretty%20much%20forced%20to%20assemble%20large%20parcels%20of%20land%20to%20accommodate%20the%20two-stair%20requirements.%20The%20apartment%20units%20in%20these%20buildings%20usually%20run%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20corridor%20that%20connects%20the%20two%20stairwells%2C%20which%20means%20the%20typical%20unit%20gets%20natural%20light%20from%20only%20one%20direction.%20A%20single-stair%20setup%20might%20allow%20units%20to%20cut%20across%20the%20building%20and%20take%20in%20light%20from%20both%20sides.%20Given%20more%20space%20to%20work%20with%2C%20developers%20could%20also%20get%20more%20creative%20with%20their%20floor%20plans%20or%20build%20bigger%20units%20with%20more%20bedrooms.%20In%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.archpaper.com%2F2023%2F03%2Fwhy-does-american-multifamily-architecture-look-so-banal-heres-one-reason%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eop-ed%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20Michael%20Eliason%2C%20a%20Seattle%20architect%20regarded%20as%20a%20leading%20voice%20in%20the%20single-stair%20movement%2C%20described%20the%20huge%20ripple%20effects%20these%20reforms%20could%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20I%20researched%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realized%20this%20one%20issue%20was%20like%20the%20Higgs%20boson%20of%20housing%2C%26quot%3B%20Eliason%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt%20connects%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20among%20those%20eager%20to%20spread%20the%20gospel%20of%20Seattle.%20The%20city%20allows%20single-stair%20buildings%20up%20to%20six%20stories%2C%20which%20opens%20up%20a%20world%20of%20possibilities.%20There%20are%20guardrails%2C%20of%20course%3A%20Under%20Seattle's%20code%2C%20single-stair%20buildings%20can't%20have%20more%20than%20four%20units%20per%20floor%2C%20and%20there%20are%20requirements%20for%20fire%20safety%20like%20an%20updated%20sprinkler%20system%20plus%20fire-resistant%20materials.%20These%20are%20all%20sensible%20precautions.%20In%20return%2C%20you%20get%20something%20like%201310%20East%20Union%20Condominiums%2C%20which%20was%20built%20on%20less%20than%203%2C000%20square%20feet%20in%20Seattle's%20Capitol%20Hill%20neighborhood.%20It%20has%20eight%20loft-style%20units%20spread%20across%20six%20stories%2C%20with%20commercial%20space%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20and%20eight%20parking%20spaces.%20A%20stairwell%20and%20elevator%20run%20down%20the%20middle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221709%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photograph%20of%201310%20East%20Union%20Condominiums%2C%20a%20seven-story%20multifamily%20building%20in%20Seattle%2C%20at%20dusk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669fba8980d4d5da13d62df7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222199%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E1310%20East%20Union%20Condominiums%20in%20Seattle%20is%20an%20example%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20single-stair%20building%20that%20would%20be%20illegal%20in%20nearly%20every%20other%20American%20city.%3Cp%3EJames%20F.%20Housel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESmall%20projects%20like%20this%20one%20are%20tough%20to%20execute%20even%20with%20one%20stairwell.%20Brian%20Court%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20the%20architecture%20firm%20the%20Miller%20Hull%20Partnership%20and%20one%20of%20the%20designers%20of%201310%20East%20Union%2C%20said%20a%20second%20staircase%20%E2%80%94%20something%20like%20200%20extra%20square%20feet%20per%20floor%20%E2%80%94%20would%20have%20made%20the%20development%20financially%20unfeasible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20trying%20to%20make%20buildings%20riskier%2C%26quot%3B%20Court%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20definitely%20need%20to%20do%20whatever%20we%20can%20and%20think%20creatively%20about%20ways%20to%20get%20more%20housing%20online%20sooner%20rather%20than%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESean%20Jursnick%2C%20a%20Denver%20architect%20and%20single-stair%20advocate%2C%20made%20a%20pilgrimage%20to%20Seattle%20last%20year%20to%20meet%20with%20Eliason%20and%20tour%20buildings%20like%201310%20East%20Union.%20City%20planners%20there%20sometimes%20call%20these%20single-stair%20buildings%20%26quot%3BSeattle%20Specials%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20they%20simply%20wouldn't%20be%20possible%20in%20pretty%20much%20any%20other%20city.%20Jursnick%20found%20more%20than%20100%20such%20developments%20in%20Seattle.%20The%20city%2C%20he%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3Bfelt%20like%20a%20good%20example%20of%20what%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20could%20unlock%20with%20a%20simple%20code%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ESeattle%20may%20be%20an%20outlier%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20it's%20pretty%20normal%20%E2%80%94%20tame%20even%20%E2%80%94%20compared%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20developed%20world.%20Almost%20all%20of%20Europe%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Asia%2C%20Mexico%20and%20South%20America%2C%20allows%20single-stair%20buildings%20of%20six%20stories%20or%20higher.%20Germany%20allows%20single-stair%20buildings%20to%20stretch%20to%20about%2020%20stories%2C%20while%20Switzerland%20has%20no%20such%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20their%20agenda%2C%20single-stair%20evangelists%20will%20have%20to%20get%20past%20one%20huge%20hypothetical%3A%20fires.%20It's%20hard%20to%20persuade%20fire%20experts%20and%20city-council%20members%20to%20loosen%20up%20the%20status%20quo%20%E2%80%94%20Americans%20are%20so%20used%20to%20two%20(or%20more)%20stairwells%20that%20anything%20less%20may%20seem%20like%20an%20unnecessary%20risk%2C%20even%20reckless.%20But%20Seattle's%20code%20offers%20a%20model%20that%2C%20by%20all%20accounts%2C%20balances%20safety%20with%20the%20very%20real%20need%20for%20more%20midrise%20housing%20on%20smaller%20lots.%20Sprinklers%2C%20fire-retardant%20materials%2C%20and%20systems%20that%20ensure%20the%20stairway%20isn't%20filled%20with%20smoke%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20fire%20have%20allowed%20Seattle%20to%20permit%20this%20kind%20of%20single-stair%20development%20for%20decades%20without%20major%20incident.%20There%20isn't%20much%20data%20on%20how%20single-stair%20buildings%2C%20specifically%2C%20have%20performed%20against%20fires%20across%20the%20world%2C%20partially%20because%20fires%20are%20relatively%20rare%20these%20days.%20But%20even%20the%20National%20Fire%20Protection%20Association%2C%20which%20has%20argued%20for%20a%20limit%20of%20four%20stories%20for%20single-stair%20residential%20buildings%2C%20recently%20reported%20that%20sprinklers%20had%20proved%20reliable%20in%20large%20fires%2C%20reducing%20death%20rates%20by%2090%25%20compared%20with%20buildings%20without%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20smaller%20buildings%20tend%20to%20be%20more%20expensive%20and%20often%20operate%20as%20condos%20rather%20than%20rentals%2C%20more%20housing%20is%20more%20housing.%20They%20could%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20as%20cities%20chart%20their%20next%20phases%20of%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Seattle%20model%20has%20already%20spread%20to%20Honolulu%2C%20and%20advocates%20around%20the%20country%20are%20making%20progress%3A%20Lawmakers%20in%20at%20least%2010%20states%2C%20including%20California%2C%20Oregon%2C%20and%20Washington%2C%20have%20either%20considered%20or%20passed%20legislation%20that%20could%20result%20in%20updated%20state%20building%20codes.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20Gannon%20told%20me%2C%20individual%20cities%20could%20adopt%20similar%20standards%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20could%20be%20something%20that%20could%20come%20in%20and%20really%20help%20us%20figure%20out%20how%20we%20urbanize.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20housing%20crisis%20demands%20creative%20solutions%2C%20but%20even%20mundane%20and%20seemingly%20small%20fixes%20can%20put%20a%20sizable%20dent%20in%20the%20country's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-outlook-shortage-home-prices-mortgage-rates-real-estate-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emassive%20housing%20deficit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20have%20plenty%20of%20real-life%20models%20for%20single-stair%20development%2C%20both%20here%20in%20the%20US%20and%20abroad.%20It's%20time%20to%20take%20the%20next%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjames-rodriguez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EJames%20Rodriguez%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20reporter%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20Discourse%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-stair-apartments-condos-housing-crisis-solution-rent-home-prices-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721813282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669eb48efb2b6bedb05957af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-stair-apartments-condos-housing-crisis-solution-rent-home-prices-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20obscure%20building%20code%20is%20ruining%20apartments%20and%20s