areer%20parting%20ways%20with%20critical%20coaches%20and%20taking%20over%20for%20Simone%20Biles%20after%20she%20withdrew%20from%20the%20Toyko%202020%20games%2C%20Chiles%20is%20focusing%20on%20herself%20at%20Paris%3B%20she%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%202023.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20put%20myself%20out%20there%3B%20I'm%20going%20to%20go%20do%20this%20and%20have%20an%20amazing%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Chiles%20said%2C%20adding%20she%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20want%20to%20regret%20anything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d895dc9b-8d76-4964-ac66-548bd60098ee%5C%22%3EWho%20is%20Jordan%20Chiles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChiles's%20star%20has%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20since%20joining%20the%20US%20gymnastics%20team%20in%202013%20when%20she%20was%2012.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%202020%20Tokyo%20Olympics%2C%20the%20Washington%20state%20native%20didn't%20qualify%20for%20individual%20finals.%20But%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjordan-chiles-thought-replacing-simone-biles-in-team-all-around-was-joke-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESimone%20Biles%20bowed%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20mental%20health%20reasons%2C%20Chiles%20stepped%20in%20to%20replace%20her%20friend%20in%20the%20all-around%20final%2C%20helping%20the%20US%20team%20win%20their%20silver%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jordan%20chiles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669926be80d4d5da13d4e7ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22727%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJordan%20Chiles%20has%20been%20a%20gymnast%20since%20the%20age%20of%20six.%3Cp%3EElsa%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20won't%20be%20surprising%20to%20anyone%20who%20knows%20Chiles'%20origin%20story.%20The%205'5%20athlete%20grew%20up%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20WA%2C%20and%20was%20named%20after%20Michael%20Jordan%2C%20according%20to%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%2