%20PIP%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20then%20offered%20a%20job%20in%20human%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20that%20case%2C%20having%20been%20in%20HR%20and%20having%20it%20happen%20to%20me%2C%20you%20can%20see%20how%20they%20are%20used%20to%20pigeonhole%20or%20to%20put%20somebody%20in%20a%20corner%2C%26quot%3B%20Rymsha%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df3d7946-d3ad-487a-b803-98f2861c8b64%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'We%20know%20we%20don't%20want%20this%20person%20at%20the%20company'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-do-to-if-put-on-pip-employment-lawyer-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPIPs%20help%20HR%20to%20cover%20itself%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20there%20were%20ever%20to%20be%20a%20legal%20issue%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERymsha%20explained%20that%20many%20of%20her%20former%20HR%20business%20partners%20hated%20putting%20people%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20spelled%20like%20we're%20doing%20this%2C%20and%20we%20know%20we%20don't%20want%20this%20person%20at%20the%20company%2C%20so%20it%20almost%20feels%20like%20a%20fool's%20errand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20had%20to%20go%20through%20the%20actions%20to%20protect%20themselves%20and%20protect%20the%20business%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20they%20were%20going%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20push%20the%20person%20out%20of%20the%20organization%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b87a2e91-be75-4805-b5d7-357b7b6a800e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuiet%20firing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Rymsha%2C%20a%20PIP%20is%20an%20invitation%20to%20leave%20a%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20get%20that%20PIP%2C%20you've%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilent-lay-offs-quiet-firing-could-backfire-companies-bosses-morale-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equiet%20fired%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20probably%20three%20to%20s