this%20leaves%20a%20very%20slim%20margin%20of%20error%20for%20the%20pilot%20because%20if%20the%20plane%20overshoots%20the%20runway%2C%20it%20will%20crash%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20airports%20in%20India%20have%20table-top%20runways%20--%20Shimla%2C%20Calicut%2C%20Mangalore%2C%20Lengpui%20(Mizoram)%20and%20Pakyong%20(Sikkim).%20Of%20these%2C%20the%20airports%20in%20Kerala%20and%20Mangalore%20have%20seen%20big%20crashes%20in%20the%20past.%C2%A0On%20May%2022%2C%202010%2C%20Air%20India%20Express%20Flight%20812%20from%20Dubai%20to%20Mangaluru%20crashed%20on%20landing%20at%20and%20158%20passengers%2C%20including%20six%20crew%20members%2C%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETen%20years%20later%2C%20on%20August%207%2C%202020%2C%20another%20table-top%20runway%20became%20the%20site%20of%20a%20tragedy.%20The%20Air%20India%20Express%20flight%20from%20Dubai%20to%20Kozhikode%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Vande%20Bharat%20mission%20to%20bring%20back%20Indian%20nationals%20stranded%20due%20to%20Covid%20pandemic.%20The%20plane%20skidded%20off%20the%20table-top%20runway%20and%20crashed%20below.%20Nineteen%20passengers%20and%20both%20pilots%20died%2C%20but%20169%20others%20survived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20Aviation%20regulator%2C%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%2C%20holds%20periodical%20reviews%20of%20table-top%20airports%20to%20ensure%20passenger%20safety.%20Back%20in%202022%2C%20an%20official%20of%20the%20DGCA%20had%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20objective%20behind%20the%20review%20was%20to%20prevent%20any%20unforeseen%20incidents%20and%20look%20for%20ways%20to%20make%20landings%20in%20these%20airports%20less%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPortugal's%20Madeira%20airport%2C%20which%20has%20a%20table-top%20runway%2C%20reported%20a%20crash%20back%20in%201977%20when%20an%20Air%20Portugal%20Flight%20425%20overshot%20and%20crashed%20onto%20a%20beach%2C%20killing%20131%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Nepal%2C%20which%20has%20a%20poor%20air%20travel%20safety%20record%2C%20has%20reported%20crashes%20involving%20table-top%20runways%20in%20the%20past.%20On%20May%2027%2C%202017%2C%20a%20cargo%20plane%20at%20crashed%20at%20the%20Tenzing-Hillary%20airport%20in%20Solukhumbu%2C%20which%20has%20such%20a%20runway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20crash%20that%20took%20place%20this%20morning%2C%20the%20Bombardier%20CRJ%20200%20flight%20skidded%20off%20the%20runway%20and%20burst%20into%20flames%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20airport%20has%20told%20NDTV.%20Tribhuvan%20airport%20in%20Kathmandu%2C%20where%20the%20crash%20took%20place%2C%20is%20on%20the%20top%20of%20a%20plateau%20and%20is%20surrounded%20by%20deep%20gorges%20and%20valleys%20on%20all%20sides.%20Kathmandu%20airport%20is%20among%20the%20most%20risky%20airports%20to%20land%20and%20was%20the%20site%20of%20a%20huge%20crash%20back%20in%201992%2C%20when%20167%20passengers%20of%20a%20Pakistan%20International%20Airlines%20plane%20had%20died.%20The%20Saurya%20Airlines%20flight%20that%20crashed%20today%20had%20crew%20and%20technical%20staff%20on%20board%20and%20was%20on%20its%20way%20to%20Pokhara.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721809320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Flve0mka8_nepal-plane-crash_625x300_24_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnepal-plane-crash-kathmandu-crash-nepal-crash-puts-spotlight-on-table-top-runways-risk-india-has-5-of-them-6176860%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20plane%20crash%20in%20Nepal%20that%20left%2018%20people%20dead%20has%20yet%20again%20put%20the%20spotlight%20on%20table-top%20runways%20that%20have%20been%20the%20site%20of%20major%20plane%20accidents%20across%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnepal-plane-crash-kathmandu-crash-nepal-crash-puts-spotlight-on-table-top-runways-risk-india-has-5-of-them-6176860%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampprojec