%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Ftodd-phillips-joker-2-surprises-with-a-daring-musical-twist%2Farticleshow%2F111982456.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nirmala%20Sitharaman's%20%26quot%3BAudacity%26quot%3B%20Counter%20To%20Trinamool's%20Budget%20Charge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20she%20presented%20Budget%202024%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20today%20countered%20the%20Opposition's%20allegations%20of%20discrimination%20in%20allocation%2C%20saying%20that%20every%20state%20cannot%20be%20named%20in%20the%20Budget%20speech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20Rajya%20Sabha%20after%20the%20Opposition%20staged%20a%20walkout%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20Opposition%2C%20particularly%20a%20senior%20leader%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20who%20stood%20up%20to%20say%20his%20views%20on%20what%20he%20heard%20of%20the%20budget%20yesterday.%20I%20would%20think%2C%20and%20maybe%20it's%20a%20bit%20too%20much%20to%20expect%2C%20that%20in%20the%20honour%20of%20democracy%2C%20at%20least%20the%20Opposition%20would%20have%20stayed%20here%20to%20listen%20to%20what%20I%20have%20to%20respond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20point%20that%20he%20(Kharge)%20raised%20that%20I%20have%20not%20named%20many%20states%2C%20and%20spoke%20about%20only%20two%20states.%20Congress%20party%20has%20been%20in%20power%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%20in%20this%20country.%20They%20have%20presented%20so%20many%20different%20budgets.%20And%20they%20would%20know%20clearly%20that%20in%20every%20budget%2C%20you%20don't%20get%20an%20opportunity%20to%20name%20every%20state%20of%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20which%20did%20not%20find%20a%20mention%20in%20her%20budget%20speech%20on%20February%201%20or%20yesterday.%20%26quot%3BThe%20cabinet%20has%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20(Narendra)%20Modi%2C%20taken%20the%20decision%20to%20set%20up%20a%20very%20big%20port%20in%20Vadhavan%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Did%20Maharashtra%20get%20ignored%20because%20I%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20name%3F%20Rs%2076%2C000%20crore%20have%20been%20announced%20for%20that%20project.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20speech%20does%20not%20mention%20a%20particular%20state%2C%20does%20it%20mean%20the%20schemes%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20the%20programmes%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20the%20external%20aided%20assistance%20we%20obtain%20don't%20go%20to%20these%20states%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20this%20is%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20by%20the%20Opposition%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20give%20an%20impression%20to%20people%20that%20nothing%20is%20being%20given%20to%20states%20ruled%20by%20non-NDA%20parties.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20challenge%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20in%20each%20of%20their%20budget%20speeches%2C%20have%20they%20named%20every%20state%20of%20this%20country.%20This%20is%20an%20outrageous%20allegation%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20some%20members%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20returned%20to%20the%20House%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20the%20TMC%20questioned%20the%20Budget%2C%20saying%20nothing%20has%20been%20given%20to%20Bengal.%20Let%20me%20highlight%20the%20fact%20that%20several%20schemes%20given%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20have%20not%20even%20been%20implemented%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20And%20you%20have%20the%20audacity%20to%20ask%20me%20now%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20members%20hit%20back%2C%20pointing%20at%20the%20unpaid%20dues%20the%20Centre%20owes%20to%20Bengal.%20Party%20MP%20Mausam%20Noor%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20floo