rquisites%20and%20allowance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vijayakumar's%20remuneration%20was%20707.46%20times%20the%20median%20salary%20of%20employees%2C%20with%20a%20median%20increase%20in%20remuneration%20of%207.07%20per%20cent%20for%20the%20year.%20In%20terms%20of%20base%20salary%2C%20he%20surpassed%20Infosys%20CEO%20Salil%20Parekh%2C%20who%20earned%20around%20Rs%2066%20crore%2C%20Wipro's%20new%20CEO%20Srini%20Pallia%2C%20who%20received%20around%20Rs%2050%20crore%2C%20and%20TCS%20CEO%20K%20Krithivasan%2C%20who%20earned%20around%20Rs%2025%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%20to%20shareholders%2C%20Mr%20Vijayakumar%20talked%20about%20the%20company's%20performance%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20closed%20the%20year%20with%20revenue%20of%20%2413.3%20billion%2C%20up%205.4%20per%20cent%20YoY%2C%20and%20an%20EBIT%20margin%20of%2018.2%20per%20cent.%26quot%3B%20HCLTech%20achieved%20the%20highest%20revenue%20growth%20rate%20among%20tier%201%20global%20IT%20services%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20company%20is%20seeing%20%26quot%3Bgreen%20shoots%26quot%3B%20in%20certain%20areas.%20He%20expects%20the%20demand%20environment%20to%20remain%20unchanged%2C%20with%20%26quot%3Bsoft%20discretionary%20spends%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20sees%20opportunities%20for%20growth%20in%20emerging%20technologies%20like%20GenAI%2C%20cloud%2C%20data%20and%20cybersecurity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHCLTech%20is%20well-positioned%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20market%20opportunities%20with%20its%20portfolio%20across%20digital%2C%20engineering%2C%20cloud%2C%20AI%20and%20software.%20The%20company%20has%20already%20delivered%20over%20200%20proofs%20of%20concept%20in%20generative%20AI%20and%20plans%20to%20train%20over%2050%2C000%20employees%20in%20FY25%20in%20Gen%20AI%20and%20similar%20capabilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20top%20four%20Indian%20IT%20companies%2C%20TCS%20led%20the%20pack%20with%20the%20highest%20revenue%20for%20FY24%20at%20Rs%202%2C40%2C8