eshow%2F111978609.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnorth-korea-does-not-care-about-trumps-words-for-kim%2Famp_articleshow%2F111978609.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Leak's%20Toxic%20Waste%20Disposal%20May%20Spark%20Health%20Crisis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENearly%2040%20years%20after%20the%20gas%20leak%20at%20Bhopal's%20Union%20Carbide%20factory%20left%20over%205%2C000%20people%20dead%20and%20severely%20affected%20thousands%20more%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20incinerating%20345%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20the%20toxic%20waste%20from%20the%20ruins%20of%20the%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20of%20Gas%20Tragedy%20Relief%20and%20Rehabilitation%20will%20oversee%20the%20waste%20treatment%20at%20a%20facility%20in%20Indore's%20Pithampur.%20The%20Centre%20has%20allocated%20Rs%20126%20crore%20for%20this%20project%2C%20set%20to%20begin%20this%20month.%20This%20waste%20is%20just%205%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20hazardous%20waste%20that%20lies%20buried%20in%20and%20around%20the%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20incineration%20facility%20in%20Pithampur%20is%20located%20close%20to%20a%20village%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20incineration%20facility%20in%20Pithampur%20is%20located%20close%20to%20a%20village%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fp8d18bqo_bhopal-gas-tragedy_625x300_24_July_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incineration%20facility%20in%20Pithampur%20is%20located%20close%20to%20a%20village%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMassive%20Health%20Risk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incineration%20of%20toxic%20waste%20is%20likely%20to%20release%20organochlorines%20in%20large%20quantities%20and%20produce%20carcinogenic%20chemicals%20such%20as%20dioxins%20and%20furans%2C%20posing%20a%20massive%20health%20risk%20to%20local%20residents%20and%20the%20environment.%20According%20to%20a%20WHO%20report%20from%20last%20year%2C%20dioxins%20%26quot%3Bare%20highly%20toxic%20and%20can%20cause%20reproductive%20and%20developmental%20problems%2C%20damage%20the%20immune%20system%2C%20interfere%20with%20hormones%20and%20also%20cause%20cancer%26quot%3B.%20It%20is%20for%20this%20reason%20that%20states%20such%20as%20Maharashtra%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Gujarat%20have%20earlier%20refused%20to%20incinerate%20this%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Jayant%20Malaiya%20and%20Gas%20Relief%20Commissioner%20Muktesh%20Varshney%20are%20among%20those%20who%20have%20voiced%20strong%20concerns%20about%20the%20environmental%20and%20health%20impacts%20of%20burning%20this%20toxic%20waste%20in%20Pithampur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20filed%20a%20Special%20Leave%20Petition%20in%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202012%2C%20opposing%20the%20incineration%20of%20the%20toxic%20waste%20in%20Pithampur.%20Concerns%20were%20raised%20about%20possible%20pollution%20of%20Yashwant%20Sagar%20Dam%2C%20a%20key%20water%20source%20for%20Indore%20city%2C%20and%20health%20risks%20to%20those%20staying%20near%20the%20incineration%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fu9aehnlo_bhopal-gas-tragedy_625x300_24_July_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Cost%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rs%20126%20crore%20investment%20is%20to%20incinerate%20just%205%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20toxic%20waste%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20huge%20monetary%20cost%20of%20this%20exercise.%20In%202012%2C%20German%20company%20GIZ%20offered%20to%20transport%20and%20incinerate%20346%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20this%20waste%20in%20Hamburg%20for%20Rs%2025%20crore.%20GIZ%20backtracked%20after%20German%20environmental%20organisations%20and%20activities%20opposed%20the%20idea%20of%20burning%20the%20waste%20in%20their%20country.%20Now%2C%20a%20much%20higher%20amount%20-%20Rs%20126%20crore%20-%20is%20being%20spent%20to%20dispose%20off%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20waste%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolluter%20pays%26quot%3B%20principle%20must%20be%20applied%20in%20this%20case%20and%20Dow%20Chemical%2C%20of%20which%20Union%20Carbide%20is%20a%20part%20now%2C%20must%20bear%20the%20cost%20for%20safe%20disposal%20of%20the%20toxic%20waste.%20Dow%20Chemical%20maintains%20that%20it%20never%20owned%20or%20operated%20the%20Bhopal%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Shah%2C%20the%20current%20Gas%20Relief%20and%20Rehabilitation%20Minister%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20I%20became%20the%20minister%2C%20we%20took%20the%20budget%20from%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20toxic%20waste%20disposal.%20We%20are%20working%20with%20the%20cooperation%20of%20the%20Centre.%20Tenders%20were%20issued%20for%20this%20work%20before%20I%20became%20the%20minister.%20We%20expect%20that%20all%20that%20the%20waste%20would%20be%20burnt%20within%20a%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Looming%20Health%20Crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20after-effects%20of%20the%20December%202%2C%201984%20gas%20leak%2C%20widely%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20industrial%20disaster%20worldwide%2C%20have%20affected%20lakhs%20across%20generations.%20Many%20children%20have%20been%20born%20with%20deformities%2C%20and%20adults%20living%20close%20to%20the%20factory%20have%20suffered%20acute%20health%20effects%20of%20toxic%20gases%20for%20life.%C2%A0The%20toxic%20waste%20has%20polluted%20groundwater%20of%2042%20settlements%20around%20the%20ruins%20of%20the%20Union%20Carbide%20factory%20with%20Persistent%20Organic%20Pollutants.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20acknowledged%20this%20and%20ordered%20the%20provision%20of%20clean%20water%20to%20the%20affected%20areas.%20Over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20this%20pollution%20has%20spread%20to%2029%20more%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Environment%20Programme%20had%20offered%20to%20assess%20the%20toxic%20waste%2C%20but%20the%20Indian%20government%20did%20not%20pursue%20this%20option.%20Since%202010%2C%20the%20government%20has%20demanded%20Rs%20350%20crore%20from%20Union%20Carbide%20and%20Dow%20Chemical%20under%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolluter%20pays%26quot%3B%20principle%20for%20the%20clean-up%20efforts%2C%20but%20to%20no%20avail.%20The%20companies%20claim%20they%20do%20not%20fall%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20Indian%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFailed%20Trial%20Runs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrial%20runs%20at%20the%20Pithampur%20facility%20to%20incinerate%20the%20waste%20have%20been%20largely%20unsuccessful%2C%20with%20six%20out%20of%20seven%20test%20runs%20failing%20and%20resulting%20in%20the%20release%20of%20toxic%20chemicals.%20Local%20organisations%20have%20warned%20of%20protests%20if%20public%20health%20is%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20Kothar%2C%20convener%20of%20Lok%20Maitri%20Sansthan%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%202012%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20the%20burning%20of%2010%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20from%20a%20South%20Indian%20factory%20that%20had%20been%20shut%20down.%20The%20waste%20matched%20Union%20Carbide's%2C%20and%20it%20was%20done%20successfully.%20The%20small%20quantity%20ensured%20positive%20monitoring%20and%20no%20health%20hazards.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20process%20that%20can%20be%20completed%20in%20a%20day.%20If%20people%20face%20any%20problems%20during%20this%2C%20it%20could%20prompt%20mass%20protests.%20We%20are%20in%20discussions%20with%20other%20organisations%20about%20this%20possibility.%20While%20the%20waste%20issue%20needs%20to%20be%20resolved%2C%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20it%20is%20right%20to%20burn%20it%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20public%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721801220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F2929ohto_bhopal-gas-tragedy_625x300_24_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-bhopal-gas-tragedy-how-disposal-of-bhopal-gas-leaks-toxic-waste-may-spark-big-health-crisis-6175821%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%2040%20years%20after%20the%20gas%20leak%20at%20Bhopal's%20Union%20Carbide%20factory%20left%20over%205%2C000%20people%20dead%20and%20severely%20affected%20thousands%20more%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20incinerating%20345%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20the%20toxic%20waste%20from%20the%20ruins%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-bhopal-gas-tragedy-how-disposal-of-bhopal-gas-leaks-toxic-waste-may-spark-big-health-crisis-6175821%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-bhopal-gas-tragedy-how-disposal-of-bhopal-gas-leaks-toxic-waste-may-spark-big-health-crisis-6175821%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-bhopal-gas-tragedy-how-disposal-of-bhopal-gas-leaks-toxic-waste-may-spark-big-health-crisis-6175821%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%206%2C%20Flip%206%20along%20with%20new%20Samsung%20wearables%20set%20for%20sale%20today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721801001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-07%2F10%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1720622245-1987.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%