ase%20against%20the%20young%20officer%20and%20probe%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUPSC%20has%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20Delhi%20Police%20against%20Ms.%20Puja%20Manorama%20Dilip%20Khedkar%20for%20misrepresenting%20and%20falsifying%20facts%20to%20obtain%20extra%20attempts%20in%20the%20UPSC%20examinations%2C%20beyond%20the%20prescribed%20limit.%20Consequently%2C%20a%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20the%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20law%2C%20and%20investigation%20has%20been%20taken%20up%20in%20Crime%20Branch%2C%26quot%3B%20Delhi%20Police%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2016%2C%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration%20(LBSNAA)%20in%20Mussoorie%20--%20the%20apex%20training%20institution%20for%20IAS%20officers%20--%20put%20Puja%20Khedkar's%20training%20on%20hold%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20serious%20allegations%20against%20her.%20She%20was%20also%20asked%20to%20report%20back%20to%20the%20academy%20by%20July%2023%20i.e.%20yesterday.%20Ms%20Khedkar%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20did%20not%20report%20to%20the%20academy%2C%20citing%20personal%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar%20hit%20headlines%20after%20Pune%20collector%20Dr%20Suhas%20Diwase%20wrote%20to%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Secretary%20Sujata%20Saunik%2C%20flagging%20several%20demands%20by%20the%20young%20officer%20that%20she%20is%20not%20entitled%20to%20during%20her%20two-year%20training.%20Ms%20Khedkar%20had%20allegedly%20asked%20for%20perks%20like%20an%20office%2C%20staff%20and%20a%20government%20vehicle.%20It%20was%20also%20found%20that%20she%20used%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20tag%20and%20red-blue%20beacon%20in%20her%20private%20Audi%20car.%20Ms%20Khedkar%20was%20then%20transferred%20from%20Pune%20to%20Washim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20selection%20of%20Puja%20Khedkar%20for%20the%20civil%20service%20came%20to%20light%20after%20it%20was%20found%20that%20she%20had%20ranked%20821%20in%20the%20merit%20list.%20It%20was%20learnt%20that%20she%20had%20availed%20of%20exemption%20for%20OBC%20non-creamy%20lawyer%20and%20multiple%20disabilities.%20It%20was%20found%20that%20she%20did%20not%20appear%20for%20the%20mandatory%20medical%20check-up%20at%20AIIMS%20and%20that%20the%20UPSC%20had%20cancelled%20her%20selection.%20Later%2C%20a%20private%20facility's%20medical%20report%20was%20accepted%2C%20clearing%20the%20path%20for%20the%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20eligibility%20for%20relaxed%20selection%20criteria%20as%20an%20OBC%20candidate%20from%20the%20non-creamy%20layer%20also%20came%20under%20the%20lens.%20Ms%20Khedkar's%20father%20Dilip%20Khedkar%20is%20a%20former%20Maharashtra%20government%20officer%2C%20who%20is%20now%20facing%20a%20corruption%20case%20and%20has%20been%20suspended%20twice%20in%20the%20past%20over%20related%20charges%2C%20including%20extortion.%20Puja%20Khedkar's%20mother%20Manorama%20Khedkar%2C%20a%20sarpanch%2C%20is%20also%20in%20trouble%20after%20a%20video%20showed%20her%20brandishing%20a%20gun%20and%20threatening%20a%20group%20of%20people.%20She%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20an%20Arms%20Act%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721799900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F8lvtkuho_puja-khedkar_625x300_12_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuja-khedkar-fails-to-meet-deadline-to-report-at-ias-training-academy-6175818%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trainee%20IAS%20officer%20Puja%20Khedkar%20is%20missing.%20The%2034-year-old%2C%20who%20has%20come%20under%20the%20scanner%2C%20for%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20her%20selection%20for%20civil%20service%2C%20was%20to%20report%20at%20the%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20National%20Academy%20Of%20Administration%20in%20Mussoorie%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuja-khedkar-fails-to-meet-deadline-to-report-at-ias-training-academy-6175818%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv