2Fril-gets-us-nod-to-resume-crude-imports-from-venezuela-despite-sanctions-124072400159_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fril-gets-us-nod-to-resume-crude-imports-from-venezuela-despite-sanctions-124072400159_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fril-gets-us-nod-to-resume-crude-imports-from-venezuela-despite-sanctions-124072400159_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Budget%202024%3A%20Allies%20In%20Good%20Humor%2C%20Marginal%20Relief%20For%20Middle%20Class%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Frqg27s78_nirmala_625x300_23_July_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20has%20presented%20the%20first%20budget%20of%20Modi%203.0%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20four%20major%20segments%3A%20'Garib'%20(Poor)%2C%20'Mahilayen'%20(Women)%2C%20'Yuva'%20(Youth)%2C%20and%20'Annadata'%20(Farmer).%20The%20budget%20reflects%20the%20mandate%20of%202024%20by%20addressing%20critical%20concerns%20while%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20for%20a%20developed%20India%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20keeping%20crucial%20allies%20like%20the%20JDU%20and%20the%20TDP%20in%20good%20humour%2C%20the%20government%20has%20recognized%20unemployment%20as%20one%20of%20the%20foremost%20challenges%20facing%20the%20country%2C%20while%20offering%20modest%20tax%20relief%20to%20middle-class%20taxpayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20budget%20underscores%20the%20reality%20that%20it's%20an%20NDA%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20not%20just%20the%20BJP's.%20With%20dependencies%20on%20allies%20like%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20have%20received%20special%20mentions%20and%20allocations%20in%20the%20budget.%20Together%2C%20their%2028%20MPs%20out%20of%20293%20NDA%20MPs%2C%20comprising%2010%25%20of%20the%20coalition%2C%20wield%20considerable%20influence.%20Both%20parties%2C%20despite%20their%20demands%20for%20special%20status%20being%20technically%20unfeasible%2C%20have%20secured%20substantial%20packages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Bihar%20And%20Andhra%20Got%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar's%20allocations%20include%20the%20Purvodaya%20project%2C%20an%20industrial%20node%20at%20Gaya%2C%20road%20connectivity%20initiatives%2C%20expressways%20totalling%20Rs.%2026%2C000%20crore%2C%20and%20power%20projects%20costing%20Rs.%2021%2C400%20crore%2C%20alongside%20Rs.%2011%2C500%20crore%20for%20flood%20relief.%20K%20C%20Tyagi%2C%20JD(U)%20advisor%20and%20chief%20national%20spokesperson%2C%20expressed%20satisfaction%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20very%20pleased%20with%20Bihar's%20provisions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20receives%20Rs.%2015%2C000%20crore%20for%20reconstruction%2C%20additional%20funds%20for%20the%20Polavaram%20Project%2C%20investments%20in%20the%20Vizag%20Chennai%20Industrial%20Corridor%2C%20and%20special%20funds%20for%20seven%20backward%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20from%20the%20opposition%20have%20labelled%20the%20budget%20as%20favouring%20Bihar%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20disproportionately.%20However%2C%20the%20government%20has%20refrained%20from%20making%20announcements%20for%20states%20with%20impending%20elections%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Jammu-Kashmir%2C%20aiming%20to%20avoid%20electoral%20motivations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMiddle%20Class%20Gets%20Some%20Relief%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost-poll%20studies%20by%20CSDS%20indicate%20a%203%25%20decrease%20in%20middle-class%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20compared%20to%202019.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20the%20government%20has%20raised%20the%20standard%20deduction%20limit%20from%20Rs.%2050%2C000%20to%20Rs.%2075%2C000%20annually%20and%20adjusted%20tax%20slabs%20for%20incomes%20up%20to%20Rs.%2012%20lakh%2C%20resulting%20in%20annual%20savings%20of%20Rs.%2017%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20increase%20in%20long-term%20capital%20gains%20tax%20from%2010%25%20to%2012.5%25%20has%20dampened%20the%20middle%20class's%20sentiment.%20The%20move%20is%20perceived%20as%20a%20message%20to%20mitigate%20inequality%2C%20especially%20among%20those%20feeling%20excluded%20from%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20stock%20market%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFood%20Inflation%20And%20Unemployment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnemployment%2C%20along%20with%20inflation%2C%20emerged%20as%20foremost%20concerns%20during%20the%20elections.%20The%20reduced%20support%20for%20the%20NDA%20in%20key%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Karnataka%20among%20the%20youth%20demographics%20(18-25%20years%20and%2026-35%20years)%20underscores%20the%20gravity%20of%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Budget%20allocates%20%E2%82%B910%2C000%20crore%20for%20a%20'price%20stabilisation%20fund'%20aimed%20at%20curbing%20food%20inflation.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20the%20Economic%20Survey%2C%20India%20needs%20to%20create%2078.5%20lakh%20jobs%20annually%20until%202036%20to%20meet%20the%20demands%20of%20its%20growing%20workforce.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20budget%20places%20a%20strong%20emphasis%20on%20job%20creation%20and%20skill%20development.%20Five%20schemes%2C%20with%20a%20total%20outlay%20of%20%E2%82%B92%20lakh%20crore%2C%20have%20been%20launched%20to%20educate%2C%20employ%2C%20and%20skill%20youth%20entering%20the%20job%20market%2C%20benefiting%20over%204.1%20crore%20individuals%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20initiative%20will%20provide%20internship%20opportunities%20at%20500%20leading%20companies%20for%201%20crore%20students%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20with%20each%20student%20receiving%20a%20monthly%20stipend%20of%20%E2%82%B95%2C000%20and%20a%20one-time%20assistance%20payment%20of%20%E2%82%B96%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20initiatives%20in%20skill%20development%20aim%20to%20train%2020%20lakh%20youth%20over%20five%20years%2C%20aiming%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20industry%20demand%20and%20the%20current%20workforce's%20capabilities%2C%20thereby%20enhancing%20youth%20employability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20expectations%20in%20certain%20quarters%2C%20the%20government%20has%20not%20introduced%20direct%20cash%20transfers%20for%20women%20or%20youth%2C%20nor%20has%20it%20increased%20support%20under%20the%20PM%20Kisan%20Nidhi%20scheme.%20This%20stance%20underscores%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20economic%20philosophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAllocations%20For%20Other%20Sectors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20ambitious%20%E2%82%B911.11%20lakh%20crore%20has%20been%20earmarked%20for%20capital%20expenditure%2C%20continuing%20the%20government's%20focus%20on%20top-down%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20create%20jobs%20and%20stimulate%20economic%20growth%20through%20multiplier%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20rural%20and%20agricultural%20distress%20apparent%20from%20recent%20electoral%20outcomes%2C%20the%20budget%20has%20allocated%20%E2%82%B91.52%20lakh%20crore%20for%20agriculture%20spending%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20%E2%82%B911%2C318%20crore%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%20Additionally%2C%20rural%20spending%20has%20been%20raised%20by%20over%2010%25%20to%20%E2%82%B92.66%20lakh%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20government%20is%20acknowledging%20unemployment%20as%20a%20significant%20concern%20among%20the%20youth%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20has%20taken%20proactive%20steps%20to%2