3Cstrong%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20look%20to%20cure%20anything%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20helped%20Bhavana%20was%20when%2C%20instead%20of%20looking%20at%20her%20caregiving%20as%20a%20way%20of%20healing%20the%20person%20(which%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20possible)%2C%20she%20began%20to%20see%20it%20as%20a%20way%20of%20helping%20them.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20that%20the%20person%20you%E2%80%99re%20caring%20for%20should%20have%20a%20full%20life.%20You%20have%20to%20remember%20that%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20is%20adding%20life%20to%20their%20days%20and%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20purpose%20of%20life%20is%20judged%20by%20how%20you%20helped%20others%20live%20theirs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fcaregiving-1-1721117570.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20corporate%20model%20of%20Caregiver%20Saathi%20involves%20working%20closely%20with%20organisations%20and%20teams%20to%20create%20a%20more%20caregiver-friendly%20environment%20in%20the%20workspace%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fcaregiving-1-1721117570.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fcaregiving-1-1721117570-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fcaregiving-1-1721117570-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fcaregiving-1-1721117570-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fcaregiving-1-1721117570-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357077%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20corporate%20model%20of%20Caregiver%20Saathi%20involves%20working%20closely%20with%20organisations%20and%20teams%20to%20create%20a%20more%20caregiver-friendly%20environment%20in%20the%20workspace%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Bhavana%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFind%20your%20balance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20let%20the%20brutality%20of%20it%20all%20get%20to%20you%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20makes%20you%20numb.%20%E2%80%9CEmpathy%20fatigue%20is%20not%20the%20way%20to%20deal%20with%20grief.%20Instead%2C%20find%20ways%20to%20be%20compassionate%20to%20support%20someone%20who%20is%20vulnerable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhavana%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20balance%20is%20where%20the%20beauty%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransform%20your%20grief%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20her%20journey%20has%20taught%20her%20anything%20it%20is%20that%20grief%20is%20a%20powerful%20resource.%20But%20instead%20of%20becoming%20a%20victim%2C%20she%20says%2C%20the%20key%20is%20to%20go%20through%20the%20situation%20in%20a%20meaningful%20fashion%20that%20will%20help%20you%20transform%2C%20not%20just%20your%20life%20but%20the%20lives%20of%20others%20too.%20%E2%80%9CAccept%20vulnerability%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20college%20years%2C%20I%20often%20had%20no%20one%20to%20talk%20to%20about%20what%20I%20was%20going%20through.%20But%20if%20you%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F180131%2Findia-women-divorce-support-group-vandana-shah-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20support%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20turn%20to%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20are%20a%20caregiver%20even%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriter%20and%20activist%20Rosalynn%20Carter%20once%20said%20that%20there%20are%20only%20four%20kinds%20of%20people%20in%20this%20world%20%E2%80%94%20those%20who%20have%20been%20caregivers%2C%20t