%20environment%2C%20with%20classrooms%20surrounded%20by%20courtyards%20and%20numerous%20open%20areas%20promoting%20both%20focused%20study%20and%20collaborative%20activities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDesigning%20the%20Titan%20Integrity%20office%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opportunity%20to%20design%20the%20Titan%20Integrity%20office%20came%20through%20a%20closed%20competition%20organised%20by%20Titan%20Company%20Ltd%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20six%20architects%2C%20Swetha%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-41-1-1721389363.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20office%20is%20wrapped%20around%20by%20trees%20with%20a%20bio%20lake%20flowing%20through%20it%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-41-1-1721389363.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-41-1-1721389363-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-41-1-1721389363-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-41-1-1721389363-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-41-1-1721389363-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357699%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20office%20is%20wrapped%20around%20by%20trees%20with%20a%20bio%20lake%20flowing%20through%20it%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20presented%20two%20distinct%20options%2C%20and%20the%20company%20selected%20the%20second%20option%20based%20on%20its%20response%20to%20the%20bioph