%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-13-at-17.31.31-1721385483-500x411.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-13-at-17.31.31-1721385483-150x123.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357671%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22416%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJigyasu%20Agarwal.%20Co-founder%2C%20Rebounce%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20their%20market%20readiness%20programme%2C%20which%20is%20paid%2C%20Rebounce%20also%20conducts%20free%20webinars%20and%20master%20classes%20on%20public%20policy%2C%20impact%20consulting%2C%20political%20consulting%2C%20the%20development%20sector%2C%20resume%20writing%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20started%20a%20podcast%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Plan%20B%20Diaries%E2%80%99%20where%20they%20speak%20to%20successful%20ex-UPSC%20aspirants%20who%20now%20work%20in%20places%20like%20the%20World%20Bank.%20They%20plan%20to%20launch%20upskilling%20courses%20soon.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETheir%20aim%20is%20to%20help%20aspirants%20shine%20in%20any%20boardroom.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20fighting%20in%20boardrooms%20of%20various%20organisations%20by%20explaining%20what%20we%20bring%20to%20the%20table%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jigyasu%20emphatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wants%20ex-UPSC%20aspirants%20to%20realise%20that%20this%20exam%20is%20a%20means%20and%20not%20an%20end.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20start%20your%20civil%20services%20preparation%2C%20have%20a%20number%20of%20attempts%20in%20your%20mind.%20If%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%2C%20find%20another%20path%20to%20reach%20your%20final%20goal.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20support%20you%20in%20making%20a%20smooth%20transition%20to%20a%20satisfying%20and%20fulfilling%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGargi%2C%20who%20secured%20positions%20in%20two%20well-known%20fellowships%2C%20Teach%20For%20India%20and%20SBI%20Youth%20for%20India%2C%