-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Adiem%20Kaanan%20Farmstay%20is%20a%20sustainable%20homestay%20in%20Nashik%20village%20made%20with%20bamboo%20and%20mud%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Disha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EYour%20chance%20to%20experience%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20at%20the%20Adiem%20Kaanan%20Farmstay%2C%20brace%20yourself%20for%20a%20packed%20schedule.%20Bird%20watching%20in%20the%20early%20morning%2C%20followed%20by%20lazing%20and%20gorging%20on%20a%20Maharashtrian%20fiesta%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20followed%20by%20peacock%20spotting%20in%20the%20evening%20and%20long%20walks%20to%20digest%20the%20hearty%20meals%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20tight%20schedule%20indeed!%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20up%20to%20you%20to%20find%20time%20for%20the%20most%20prized%20activity%20the%20farmstay%20offers%20%E2%80%94%20fruit%20plucking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rewarding%20session%20begins%20with%20taking%20a%20basket%20out%20into%20the%20fields%20and%20then%20filling%20it%20with%20the%20choicest%20selection%20of%20lychees%2C%20gooseberries%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejamun%20%3C%2Fem%3E(java%20plum)%2C%20%3Cem%3Efalsa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20small%2C%20dark%2C%20purple%20fruit%20with%20a%20sweet%20and%20sour%20taste)%2C%20apples%2C%20pears%2C%20oranges%20and%20more.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291911%2Fbest-fruit-picking-farms-in-india-for-family-vacation-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efruit%20plucking%20activity%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecomes%20highly%20recommended%20by%20Disha%20who%20has%20spent%20much%20of%20her%20youth%20engaged%20in%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-6-1721041397.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%2