0for%20ourselves.%20If%20this%20becomes%20aspirational%20and%20households%20use%20sunlight%20as%20energy%20then%20collectively%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20mitigate%20the%20climate%20crisis.%20All%20of%20us%20can%20think%20of%20adopting%20solar%20cooking%20as%20our%20first%20step%20towards%20energy%20self-sufficiency%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESource%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fenergy%2Foil-gas%2Flpg-imports-surge-60-in-five-years%2Farticleshow%2F107732630.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELPG%20imports%20surge%2060%25%20in%20five%20years%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3EBy%20Sanjeev%20Choudhary%20for%20Economic%20Times%2C%20published%20on%2016%20February%202024.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Reva%20Jhingan%20Malik.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721209794000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-cooking-1-1721205550.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D357212%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reva%20Jhingan%20Malik%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20uses%20solar%20energy%20to%20cook%20all%20her%20meals.%20She%20explains%20how%20she%20replaced%20an%20LPG%20stove%20with%20a%20solar%20cooker%20to%20move%20towards%20sustainable%20practices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357212%2Fsolar-cooker-vs-lpg-stove-cylinder-how-to-use-for-cooking-reva-malik-saves-money-with-solar-energy%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99m%20Their%20Mother%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20This%2072-YO%20Built%20a%20Safe%20Space%20for%20150%20Kids%20With%20HIV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20Mangal%20Shah%20from%20Mah