Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20kick-start%20the%20process%2C%20Shweta%20suggests%20preparing%20the%20right%20potting%20mix.%20She%20recommends%20mixing%2050%20percent%20soil%2C%2030%20percent%20compost%2C%20and%2020%20percent%20coco%20peat%20to%20prepare%20a%20potting%20mix%20that%20will%20ensure%20vegetables%20receive%20sufficient%20nutrition%20for%20growth.%20Adding%20homemade%20manure%20or%20vermicompost%20to%20this%20mix%20enhances%20the%20soil%E2%80%99s%20fertility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20the%20top%20five%20vegetables%20that%20thrive%20in%20the%20rainy%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Tomatoes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETomatoes%20are%20perfect%20for%20beginners.%20They%20can%20be%20grown%20in%20small%20containers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECut%20small%20slices%20of%20tomatoes%20or%20simply%20add%20seeds%20to%20a%20small%20pot.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECover%20them%20lightly%20with%20soil%20and%20sprinkle%20water%2C%20maintaining%20consistent%20moisture.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWater%20the%20plant%20regularly%2C%20but%20if%20the%20soil%20is%20moist%2C%20you%20can%20water%20at%20intervals%20of%20one%20or%20two%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKeep%20the%20seedlings%20out%20of%20direct%20sunlight%20and%20rainwater.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20the%20plant%20grows%2C%20add%20homemade%20manure.%20You%20can%20prepare%20a%20natural%20fertiliser%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fhow-to-turn-pomegranate-mango-orange-peels-into-fertilisers-for-your-garden%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efruit%20peels%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Soak%20the%20peels%20in%20water%20for%20a%20week%2C%20then%20strain%20out%20the%20water%20and%20add%20it%20to%20the%20plants.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUse%20cow%20dung%20fertiliser%20during%20the%20flowering%20stage.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20tomatoes%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20harvest%20in%20about%20three%20months.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Pumpkin%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPumpkins%20can%20be%20planted%20during%20July-August.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESow%20seeds%20in%20a%20seedling%20tray%3B%20the%20seeds%20will%20germinate%20within%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETransfer%20them%20to%20a%20large%20container%20as%20they%20grow.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPlant%20only%20one%20sapling%20in%20a%20container.%20You%20can%20grow%20this%20vine%20crop%20in%20a%2024-inch%20pot.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFlowering%20will%20start%20in%2030%20days%2C%20and%20pumpkins%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20harvest%20in%20about%2090%20days%20from%20planting.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjuly-vegetables-5-1656927723-1721135593.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ridge%20gourd%20plant%20will%20start%20yielding%20in%20about%20four%20months.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjuly-vegetables-5-1656927723-1721135593.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjuly-vegetables-5-1656927723-1721135593-300x170.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjuly-vegetables-5-1656927723-1721135593-500x283.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjuly-vegetables-5-1656927723-1721135593-768x435.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjuly-vegetables-5-1656927723-1721135593-150x85.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357149%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22680%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20ridge%20gourd%20plant%20will%20start%20yielding%20in%20about%20four%20months.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdi